\cf0 High-Light is a text formatting plugin for styled textareas in RapidWeaver. This means that you can use it in any textarea that accepts styled text. Besides the obvious 
\f5\i \'d2Styled Text\'d3
\f1\i0  pagestyle it also includes most (if not all) of the built-in and third-party pagestyles for RapidWeaver. The only places where you cannot use it is the 
\f5\i \'d2HTML\'d3
\f1\i0  pagestyle and the various special fields for a page (e.g. 
\f5\i \'d2Title\'d3
\f1\i0 , 
\f5\i \'d2Browser title\'d3
\f1\i0 , the fields in the 
\f5\i \'d2Contact form\'d3
\f1\i0  etc.). So the possibilities for where you can use this plugin are enormous.\
